<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-02 15:18 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1155 &Cx1f; taf-z
u v AM-ADD-NYT-BUDGET &LR;      07-02 0807
