<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-R-HARRY-POTTER-FRENZY-ART-2TAKES-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
A FRENZIED WEEKEND LIES AHEAD FOR FOURTH BOOK IN HARRY POTTER
SERIES 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (REPEATING to add photo note; no other changes.)  (Eds., name Sage-EL in last graf is CQ) 
(ART ADV: Photo NYT7 is being sent to NYT photo clients.
Nonsubscribers can purchase one-time rights by calling 888-603-1036
or 888-346-9867.) 
 By BERNARD WEINRAUB   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES _ Planes gliding over beaches on Long Island and the
Jersey Shore as well as in Los Angeles, Chicago and Hilton Head,
S.C., will carry banners this coming Saturday reading, ```Harry
